text: Obrastsovo-Travino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Obrastsovo-Travinsky Selsoviet, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 2,730 as of 2010. There are 31 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kamyzyaksky District
title: Obrastsovo-Travino
